settings.name: content
settings.value: Our tool, designed as an extension for Visual Studio Code and built on top of the Impact Framework, is a revolutionary step towards a more sustainable future in software development. By simplifying the coding process, reducing duplication, and identifying potential security vulnerabilities, our tool helps developers create more efficient, secure, and environmentally friendly software.
settings.computedValue: Our tool, designed as an extension for Visual Studio Code and built on top of the Impact Framework, is a revolutionary step towards a more sustainable future in software development. By simplifying the coding process, reducing duplication, and identifying potential security vulnerabilities, our tool helps developers create more efficient, secure, and environmentally friendly software.

settings.name: content
settings.value:
Given a win, we plan to make the following major enhancements to our tool:

  1. Extend Language Support: Currently, our tool supports Python, one of the most popular programming languages. We plan to extend this support to all programming languages, enabling us to help a broader range of developers create more sustainable software.
  2. Improve User Interface: We aim to enhance the user experience by making our tool more intuitive and easier to use. This will enable developers of all skill levels to fully utilize our tool and contribute to more sustainable software development.
  3. Introduce New Features: Based on user feedback and needs, we plan to introduce new features to our tool. This could include advanced code analysis capabilities, more comprehensive security checks, and other features that help developers create more efficient and sustainable software.
